---
description: Standards for working with prompt files
globs: "**/*.prompt"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Follow the naming convention: <basename>_<language>.prompt or <basename>_LLM.prompt
  - Use _LLM suffix for model-specific prompts
  - Use _python, _bash, etc. for language-specific prompts
- Structure prompt files clearly with consistent sections
- When referencing variables in prompt templates, use {placeholders} format
- Test prompt changes with the `pdd preprocess` command before committing
- For complex prompts that require structured output, consider using XML tags
